Syrian-Caramanian Line. Port Said, Jaffa, Beyrout,
                        Tripoli, Alexandretta, Mersina, Febr. 18;
                            March 4, 18 ; April 1. 15, 29 ; May 13, 27 ;
                            June 10, 24.

Three regicide officers attacked two tepn'ies with swords in the
                                streets of the city. A fierce fight ensued in which a deputy was
                                dangerously wounded. (Reuter}
